    /*:.+.*.*:.*..:..*.*:.*..:.+.*.*:*/
    /*              DATE TIME ARITHMETIC OPERATIONS               */
    /*.:.+.*.:*.*.+.:*.*..:.:.*.:*.+.*/

    /// @dev Adds `numYears` to the unix timestamp, and returns the result.
    /// Note: The result will share the same Gregorian calendar month,
